<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">函電</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">與慈雲法師書（四通）</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">四</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<milestone unit="juan" n="57"/>
<pb ed="TX" xml:id="TX26.0017.0105a" n="0105a"/>
<lb ed="TX" n="0105a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">與茗山書</cb:mulu><head>與茗山書</head>
<lb ed="TX" n="0105a02"/><p xml:id="pTX26p0105a0201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">茗山：二月函報等均悉。前所通知訓練班已暫停辦，爾專心在湘省辦佛教會，及
<lb ed="TX" n="0105a03"/>邀明真法師等辦佛學院為宜。余病軀專需休養，不能任繁劇也。全湘佛教繫座下，謙
<lb ed="TX" n="0105a04"/>忍集賢能，勉之！太虛。六、十五。</p><byline cb:type="other">（茗山存稿）</byline></cb:div>
